'\u00d6zge Ya\u011fiz''' is a Turkish TV actress known for ''[[Yemin]]'' (2019) and ''Adini sen koy'' (2016).\n\n== Education ==\nShe graduated from [[Ba\u015fkent University]] with a degree in communication sciences <ref name=\"education\">{{cite news|url=https://www.sozcu.com.tr/hayatim/magazin-haberleri/ozge-yagiz-kimdir-ozge-yagiz-nereli-ve-kac-yasinda-szcu3/|title=Biography}}</ref>. She studied acting at No.10 Studios.\n\n== Film and TV work ==\n\n\u00d6zge is the female lead on the TV show ''[[Yemin]]'' 2019, which is directed by Ayhan \u00d6zen, which is currently into its second season, and airs on Kanal 7. She previously acted in ''Adini Sen Koy'' (2016) as Zeliha along with other co-stars Hazal Subasi and Yaprak Durmaz.\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Work\n!Role\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Adini sen koy]]''\n|Zeliha\n|-\n|2019\n|''[[Yemin]]''\n|Reyhan\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|1}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Instagram|ozgeyagizz}}\n* {{IMDb name|10497761}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Yagiz, \u00d6zge}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:21st-century Turkish actresses]]\n", "name_user": "Vinaykumar89.iitkgp", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%96zge_Ya%C4%9F%C4%B1z"}
